OL,6,FHer family told an inquest her spiral
OL,7,Finto mental health decline and PTSD
OL,8,Fdated exactly from the alleged
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FThe man she accused was later
OL,12,Fconvicted of child sex offences.
OL,14,FThe to the Criminal Justice Bill which
OL,15,Fis currently going through parliament.
OL,17,FThe new rules would also mean that
OL,18,Fsexual violence investigations must be
OL,19,Fconducted in line with national
OL,20,Fguidelines which are already taken up
OL,21,Fby the College of Policing.
