OL,4,Cassault victims after death of teenager
OL,6,FSince her death, her family have been
OL,7,Fcampaigning for the introduction of
OL,8,FGaia's Principle where officers would
OL,9,Fautomatically have to "join the dots"
OL,10,Fbetween any similar allegations
OL,11,Fagainst the same suspect, rather than
OL,12,Ftreating everything in isolation.
OL,14,FGaia's cousin, Marienna Pope-Weidemann
OL,15,Ffrom the Gemini Project said: "It will
OL,16,Flegally compel officers, who are
OL,17,Finvestigating rape or serious sexual
OL,18,Foffences, to do a thorough background
OL,19,Fcheck on suspects and check for
OL,20,Findependent allegations against them.
