OL,6,F"A significant number of perpetrators
OL,7,Fwe know are serial offenders and have
OL,8,Fmultiple victims."
OL,10,FA police project called Operation
OL,11,FSoteria, which aims to put victims at
OL,12,Fthe heart of investigations, suggests
OL,13,Fbetween 40 and 59% of offenders are
OL,14,Flinked to multiple offences.
OL,16,F"We need this level of accountability
OL,17,Fin a country where less than 1.5% of
OL,18,Frape cases result in a charge," said
OL,19,FGaia's cousin Marienna.
